OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778850694
OL,3,CSouthport survivor 'devastated' after
OL,4,CNHS staff accessed records without
OL,5,Creason
OL,7,FA survivor of the Southport attack has
OL,8,Faccused senior hospital officials of a
OL,9,F"cover up" after it was revealed
OL,10,Falmost 50 members of staff hospital
OL,11,Fworkers looked at the medical records
OL,12,Fof victims for no reason.
OL,14,FLeanne Lucas, who was the instructor
OL,15,Fat the Taylor Swift-themed dance
OL,16,Fworkshop targeted by the 17-year-old
OL,17,Fattacker in July 2024, said she is
OL,18,F"devastated and horrified" to learn
OL,19,Fher medical records were accessed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778850694
OL,3,CSouthport survivor 'devastated' after
OL,4,CNHS staff accessed records without
OL,5,Creason
OL,7,FThree girls ` Alice da Silva Aguiar,
OL,8,Fnine, Bebe King, six, and Elsie Dot
OL,9,FStancombe, seven ` were murdered by
OL,10,FRudakubana at The Hart Space, while 10
OL,11,Fothers were injured.
OL,13,FSome of those injured were treated at
OL,14,Fhospitals under the University
OL,15,FHospitals of Liverpool Group, where an
OL,16,Finformation access audit carried out
OL,17,Fby the trust found 48 staff accessed
OL,18,Ftheir records without good reason.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778850694
OL,3,CSouthport survivor 'devastated' after
OL,4,CNHS staff accessed records without
OL,5,Creason
OL,7,FLeanne Lucas, who now campaigns
OL,8,Fagainst knife crime, says medical
OL,9,Fstaff invaded her privacy when she was
OL,10,Fat her most vulnerable.
OL,12,FShe said: "Nothing will take away my
OL,13,Fgratitude to the staff who saved my
OL,14,Flife, but 48 people not involved in my
OL,15,Fcare abused their position of trust to
OL,16,Faccess the files of victims who have
OL,17,Fsuffered unspeakable trauma.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778850694
OL,3,CSouthport survivor 'devastated' after
OL,4,CNHS staff accessed records without
OL,5,Creason
OL,7,F"The decision to keep this from me for
OL,8,Falmost two years is a new low. I am
OL,9,Fspeaking out as I want this scandal
OL,10,Fand the attempted cover up by senior
OL,11,Fmanagement exposed for what it is."
OL,13,FThe audit was carried out just days
OL,14,Fafter the attack, but this information
OL,15,Fwas not given to the patients involved
OL,16,Funtil May 2026.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778850694
OL,3,CSouthport survivor 'devastated' after
OL,4,CNHS staff accessed records without
OL,5,Creason
OL,7,FNicola Brook, a legal director at law
OL,8,Ffirm Broudie Jackson Canter, which is
OL,9,Frepresenting three survivors including
OL,10,FMs Lucas at the Southport Inquiry,
OL,11,Fsaid: "This is a truly unbelievable
OL,12,Fbreach of privacy for victims of one
OL,13,Fof the most horrific attacks this
OL,14,Fcountry has ever seen.
OL,16,F"This is more than a few bad apples
OL,17,Fwhen it was 48 different members of
OL,18,Fstaff who, for no legitimate reason,
OL,19,Fchose to access vulnerable victims'
OL,20,Frecords.
OL,26,@sD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778850694
OL,3,CSouthport survivor 'devastated' after
OL,4,CNHS staff accessed records without
OL,5,Creason
OL,7,F"That speaks to a culture and one that
OL,8,Fwill only change if there are real
OL,9,Fconsequences for those responsible."
OL,11,FAccording to the HSJ, University
OL,12,FHospitals of Liverpool Group reported
OL,13,Fthe incident to the Information
OL,14,FCommissioner's Office in August 2024.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778850694
OL,3,CSouthport survivor 'devastated' after
OL,4,CNHS staff accessed records without
OL,5,Creason
OL,7,FTrust chief executive James Sumner
OL,8,Fsaid after it had concluded its
OL,9,Finvestigation, it had made the
OL,10,Fdecision not to inform the patients
OL,11,Finvolved after "taking into
OL,12,Fconsideration the potential
OL,13,Fpsychological impact it may have upon
OL,14,Fthem at the time".
OL,16,FHe said the trust had "notified the
OL,17,Frelevant regulators and professional
OL,18,Fbodies", including the ICO, and "were
OL,19,Ffully transparent about any findings
OL,20,Fand actions taken".
OL,26,@sD@POUvD@QO]xD@WOUzD@GO]zD@aOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778850694
OL,3,CSouthport survivor 'devastated' after
OL,4,CNHS staff accessed records without
OL,5,Creason
OL,7,FMr Sumner said: "We are sincerely
OL,8,Fsorry for any distress that may have
OL,9,Fbeen caused to the patients that were
OL,10,Funder our care and who trusted us to
OL,11,Flook after them when they were most
OL,12,Fvulnerable.
OL,14,F"Breaches of patient confidentiality
OL,15,Fare inexcusable and undermine the hard
OL,16,Fwork of those teams who sought to
OL,17,Fprovide the highest standard of care
OL,18,Fto these patients after they
OL,19,Fexperienced such traumatic and life-
OL,20,Fchanging events.
OL,26,@oD@QOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778850694
OL,3,CSouthport survivor 'devastated' after
OL,4,CNHS staff accessed records without
OL,5,Creason
OL,7,F"Staff who were found to access
OL,8,Fpatient records inappropriately were
OL,9,Fsubject to HR disciplinary processes."
OL,11,FLeanne Lucas suffered serious injuries
OL,12,Fwhen she was stabbed while trying to
OL,13,Fprotect two little girls.
OL,15,FAxel Rudakubana was jailed for a
OL,16,Fminimum of 52 years for the murders of
OL,17,Fthe three girls and attempted murders
OL,18,Fof eight other children, who cannot be
OL,19,Fnamed for legal reasons, as well as Ms
OL,20,FLucas and businessman John Hayes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
